text: S&M; Airlines is the second studio album by American punk rock band, NOFX. S&M; Airlines was released on September 5, 1989. The producer of the album was Brett Gurewitz. The last track on the album is a cover of the Fleetwood Mac song, "Go On Your Way". ==Songs== Category:1989 albums Category:NOFX albums Category:Punk albums
title: S&M Airlines
